  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong>&nbsp;Striker. You dart in to attack, do massive damage, and then retreat to safety. You do best when teamed with a defender to flank enemies.</p>\n<p><strong>Power Source:&nbsp;</strong> Martial. Your talents depend on extensive training and constant practice, innate skill, and natural coordination</p>\n<p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dexterity</li>\n<li>Strength</li>\n<li>Charisma</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</li>\n<li>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.4JEjuSyMmf6FxmGS]{Dagger}</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.8JyDOEsRGAo0qLcN]{Hand Crossbow}</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.8suLj8aO9ijycfJO]{Shuriken}</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.qvdaVQkpFjDEzCeP]{Sling}</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.BC3aiO0JwB0OYXp5]{Short Sword}</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 Reflex</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level</strong><strong>:</strong> [[12]] + Con Score</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points&nbsp;</strong><strong>per Level Gained:</strong> [[5]]</p>\n<p><strong>Base&nbsp;</strong><strong>Healing</strong><strong>&nbsp;Surges per Day:</strong> [[6]] + Con Mod</p>\n<p><strong>Skill Training: </strong>Stealth and Thievery, choose four more from the following list:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Acrobatics (Dex)</li>\n<li>Athletics (Str)</li>\n<li>Bluff (Cha)</li>\n<li>Dungeoneering (Wis)</li>\n<li>Insight (wis)</li>\n<li>Intimidate (Cha)</li>\n<li>Perception (Wis)</li>\n<li>Streetwise (Cha)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>First Strike</li>\n<li>Rogue Weapon Talent</li>\n<li>Sneak Attack</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Choose one of the following&nbsp;Rogue Tactics:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Artful Doger</li>\n<li>Brutal Scoundrel</li>\n</ul>",
